## ğŸ“ Files

- `hollow_sign.py` â€” main program file  
- `encounter_log.txt` â€” automatically generated log of all encounters  
- `encounters.json` â€” your editable list of up to 10 encounter entries

### Example `encounters.json`:
```json
{
  "encounters": [
    { "name": "Orc Raiders", "notes": "Aggressive patrol of 3 orcs" },
    { "name": "Witch in the Trees", "notes": "Offers knowledge... for a price" }
